Real Estate Agents for Rental Properties in Rochester, New York










Our Company
Since 2002, the real estate agents at the Lighthouse Management group of companies have offered quality rental properties in Western New York to people throughout the cities of Buffalo, Niagara Falls and Rochester, NY. From apartments to whole houses, we have the real estate in Western NY you are sure to love. 

    We pride ourselves in offering clean and safe units at reasonable rates, with a wide range of options that include studios, 1- to 4-bedroom apartments, and whole houses for rent. Contact us today to request more information on any of our Rochester, Buffalo or Niagara Falls real estate selections.

Who We Are
The Lighthouse Management Group has two offices, one in Rochester and one in Buffalo, serving all of upstate New York From Niagara Falls to east of Rochester. 
  Lighthouse Management Partners, Inc. services Niagara and Erie Counties covering Niagara Falls, NY and Buffalo, NY. The office is managed by Christopher Valentine, Lic. Associate R.E. Broker. It is co-owned by Scott Seppen and Christopher Valentine.

Together, they presently manage more than 1000 units in the Western NY area, working with Investors from all over the world, including England, South Africa, and Hong Kong. Both companies are individually Licensed NYS Real Estate Brokers and members of their local real estate boards.
Contact us today to speak with a real estate agent about your property needs!


