Apartments for rent in New Jersey
Get an apartment in New Jersey and you will understand why it is called "The Garden State". Farms and horses fill the land of this beautiful state.  New Jersey, whose state's motto is "liberty and prosperity", is the most popular state to live in. It has the highest population density of any U.S. state. If you are looking for state with a nice blend of urban culture and pedestrian-friendly green space, New Jersey is the state for you. Enjoy the beauty, the many busy diners, and endless cultural activities that New Jersey has to offer.   

How would you like to rent a New Jersey apartment in Atlantic City? This city is a popular nation-wide destination for business conventioneers and tourists. Casinos, theme parks, museums, the ocean boardwalk and many cultural events are in yours to explore.  Many people like to live in New Jersey because it's such an easy commute to New York City. If you rent an apartment in Union City or Newport you can access main line train stations or bus stops within walking distance of your front door! 

If you enjoy the outdoors, New Jersey is one of the most gorgeous states to see bald eagles, red-tailed hawks, marsh hawks, ospreys, great blue herons, swans, and other wildlife in their natural environment.  Rent a New Jersey apartment near The Wharton State Forest and spend your weekends canoeing, mountain biking, horseback riding, or hiking on the Batona Trail.  If you prefer more action, join the many New York Giants fans at an exciting fall football game. If you rent an apartment in East Rutherford, home of the Giants Stadium, you might be able to hear the crowd cheering from your front porch! 

The endless stimulation of New York City is right next door if you rent an apartment in New Jersey. However, don't under estimate the excitement and charm of New Jersey's own towns.  The quarky little town of Hoboken is a haven for art lovers. Once home to Frank Sinatra, the waterfront defines Hoboken as a port town where many Hobokenites enjoy strolling the Pier. Hackensack is another unique New Jersey city to rent an apartment. Pack a picnic for the outdoor summer concert series on the courthouse green.  

New Jersey, has some of North America's most family-friendly attractions.  The kids will love Adventure Aquarium in Camden where they can see a variety of animals including jelly fish, sharks, and even a hippo exhibit. Take the family to Creambridge, NJ where you can visit Six Flags Hurricane Harbor.

New Jersey also features a number of pet-friendly apartments and many inexpensive rentals for college students, senior citizens, and families. Browse the wide variety of affordable apartment rentals in New Jersey. ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZAberdeen ApartmentsAbsecon ApartmentsAllentown ApartmentsAnnandale ApartmentsAsbury Park ApartmentsAtlantic City ApartmentsAtlantic Highlands ApartmentsAvenel ApartmentsBarnegat ApartmentsBarrington ApartmentsBasking Ridge ApartmentsBayonne ApartmentsBayville ApartmentsBelle Mead ApartmentsBelleville ApartmentsBellmawr ApartmentsBelmar ApartmentsBergenfield ApartmentsBerkeley Heights ApartmentsBerlin ApartmentsBlackwood ApartmentsBloomfield ApartmentsBloomingdale ApartmentsBordentown ApartmentsBound Brook ApartmentsBradley Beach ApartmentsBranchburg ApartmentsBrick ApartmentsBridgeton ApartmentsBridgewater ApartmentsBrielle ApartmentsBudd Lake ApartmentsBurlington ApartmentsBurlington Township ApartmentsButler ApartmentsCaldwell ApartmentsCamden ApartmentsCarneys Point ApartmentsCarteret ApartmentsCedar Grove ApartmentsCedar Knolls ApartmentsChatham ApartmentsCherry Hill ApartmentsCinnaminson ApartmentsClark ApartmentsClayton ApartmentsClementon ApartmentsCliffside Park ApartmentsCliffwood ApartmentsClifton ApartmentsClinton ApartmentsCollingswood ApartmentsColonia ApartmentsColts Neck ApartmentsCranford ApartmentsDelran ApartmentsDenville ApartmentsDeptford ApartmentsDover ApartmentsDumont ApartmentsEast Brunswick ApartmentsEast Orange ApartmentsEast Rutherford ApartmentsEast Windsor ApartmentsEastampton ApartmentsEatontown ApartmentsEdgewater ApartmentsEdgewater Park ApartmentsEdison ApartmentsElizabeth ApartmentsElmwood Park ApartmentsEnglewood ApartmentsEwing ApartmentsFair Lawn ApartmentsFlanders ApartmentsFlemington ApartmentsFlorham Park ApartmentsFort Lee ApartmentsFranklin Lakes ApartmentsFranklin Park ApartmentsFranklinville ApartmentsFreehold ApartmentsGalloway ApartmentsGalloway Township ApartmentsGarfield ApartmentsGa